# _meta.notes — Obsidian Documentation Vault

> The ultimate documentation hub for all active projects, future ideas, architecture decisions, and reusable knowledge.

---

## Purpose

This Obsidian vault serves as the **single source of truth** for:
- Project metadata and status tracking
- Technology knowledge base (concepts wiki)
- Architecture Decision Records (ADRs)
- Reusable code snippets and patterns
- Document templates for consistency
- Dynamic dashboards via Dataview

**Philosophy:** Documentation lives here. Code lives in project folders.

---

## Scope & Editing Rules

**You MAY:**
- Create/edit any `.md` file inside `_meta.notes/`
- Add new concepts, snippets, templates, project files
- Update dashboards and journal entries
- Maintain the Home.md central hub

**You MAY NOT:**
- Edit code files (those belong in project directories)
- Modify project configurations or package.json files
- Run build/test commands from here
- Make git commits (this vault may not be version-controlled)

