## File Conventions

### YAML Frontmatter (Required for Projects)

```yaml
---
type: project
status: active | alpha | maintenance | stable | live | incubating
priority: P0 | P1 | P2 | P3
tech-stack:
  - "[[Concepts/React|React]]"
  - "[[Concepts/TypeScript|TypeScript]]"
repo-path: folder-name-in-workspace
live-url: https://...
created: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
---
```

### Obsidian Linking

```markdown
# Internal links
[[Projects/Neuman Brain]]
[[Projects/Neuman Brain|Brain]]  # With alias
[[Concepts/React]]

# External file links (to code)
[[../system.knowledgebase/CLAUDE.md|Project Guidelines]]

# Dataview queries
```dataview
TABLE status, priority FROM "Projects" WHERE type = "project"
```
```

