## Maintenance Tasks

### Daily
- [ ] Update `Journal/YYYY-MM-DD.md` with session logs

### When Adding a Project
1. Create `Projects/<Name>.md` using template
2. Add to `Home.md` project table
3. Create any needed ADRs in `Decisions/`
4. Update `Dashboards/Active Projects.md` if manual entries exist

### When Learning New Tech
1. Create `Concepts/<Technology>.md`
2. Link from relevant project files
3. Add useful snippets to `Snippets/`

### When Making Architecture Decisions
1. Use `Templates/ADR - Decision Record.md`
2. Save as `Decisions/<ID>-<Title>.md`
3. Link from affected project files

